{"title":"十字岭之歌","authors":["皇甫束玉"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":8,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"十字岭之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皇甫束玉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人是英雄的人啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山是英雄的山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左权将军牺牲在这边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此这小小十字岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在历史上有了名篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在地理上成了名山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１９４２年五月天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日寇三万“扫荡”太行山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“铁壁合围”十字岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总部安危一身担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑云压城城不摧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰山压顶腰不弯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山见证："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军的伟躯屹立在山巅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他指挥若定意志坚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山花见证："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军的热血洒在万花间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它染得这山花更红更灿烂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的汉玉碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岿然竖立青松间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄美的纪念亭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翼然翘向蔚蓝的天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月的鲜花开满山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞻仰的人群肩并肩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左权将军之名昭千古，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《左权将军之歌》代代传。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}